"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/48/12035?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Vaccines (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?23/4/23619?source=see_link\">",
